  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Arctic S.A. (Arctic the &quot;company&quot;) is Romanias only producer of refrigerators, with revenues of approximately $53 million in 2002. The $50 million project consists of :
acquisition of Arctic by Arcelik, a Turkey-based home appliance leader, with a turnover of approximately $1.5 billion in 2002;
Arctics conversion into an efficient production base for Arceliks refrigerator sales in Europe.  
Arcelik will improve Arctics performance through:
implementing a modernization, quality improvement and capacity expansion program and 
restructuring Arctics existing financial liabilities.</narrative>
  </description>
